my_app/
├── presentation/
│   ├── views.py   # UI logic (web pages, templates)
│   ├── forms.py    # Input validation
│   └── __init__.py 
├── application/
│   ├── services.py   # Business logic (use cases)
│   └── __init__.py 
├── domain/
│   ├── models.py    # Core business objects
│   ├── repositories.py # Interfaces for data access
│   └── __init__.py
├── infrastructure/
│   ├── database.py   # Database implementation
│   ├── api_clients.py  # Clients for external APIs
│   └── __init__.py
├── config.py        # Configuration settings
└── main.py          # Application entry point